title: I clicked on Pixel Imprint option after providing the pattern, I didn't see "Add fingerprint" option
content: I have deleted my fingerprints and tried to add using "Pixel Imprint" option. It prompted me for the pattern and when I enter, it took me to the security screen but not to the "Add fingerprints" screen.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 3 XL
